ADDITIONAL TERMS — AI TRAINING RESTRICTION

1. Definition. "AI Model Training" means the use of the Software, in whole or
   in part, including but not limited to its source code, documentation,
   comments, structure, organization, patterns, or any derivative works
   thereof, as training data, evaluation data, or any other form of input
   for the purpose of developing, training, fine-tuning, evaluating, or
   improving any artificial intelligence, machine learning, or large language
   model system.

2. Restriction. The Software may NOT be used for AI Model Training under any
   circumstances. This restriction applies to all entities, including but not
   limited to corporations, research institutions, academic organizations,
   government agencies, and individuals.

3. Derivative Works. The AI Training Restriction applies equally to any
   derivative works, modifications, or adaptations of the Software.

4. Enforcement. Any violation of this AI Training Restriction constitutes a
   material breach of this License and shall entitle the copyright holders to
   pursue all available legal remedies, including but not limited to:

   a. Injunctive relief to immediately cease the unauthorized use;
   b. Monetary damages, including any profits attributable to the unauthorized
      use of the Software for AI Model Training;
   c. Statutory damages as provided by applicable law; and
   d. Reasonable attorneys' fees and costs of litigation.

5. Jurisdiction. Any legal action arising from a violation of this AI Training
   Restriction may be brought in any court of competent jurisdiction, and the
   violating party consents to the personal jurisdiction of such courts.

6. Severability. If any provision of this AI Training Restriction is held to
   be unenforceable or invalid, such provision shall be changed and interpreted
   to accomplish its objectives to the greatest extent possible under applicable
   law, and the remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect.

By using the Software, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and
agree to be bound by the terms of this License, including the AI Training
Restriction.
